channel.topic: Welcome to the 2024 Kerths! Check the pinned messages for the link to the stage.

messages.content:
Everyone will be able to chat over here in the main channel, which will serve as our audience. We encourage cheering and laughing and fun, but do try to keep things PG-13ish just like we do on the boards! *eyes @Darth_Michael warily*

If you have a question, don't be afraid to ask it here, even while the ceremony is going on! We want everyone to have fun and be included!

The Stage (over yonder https://discord.com/channels/908556304568684575/1231642363881848933) will only allow for admins and Ceremony Speakers to chat/send messages. If you're on a computer (desktop/laptop) or on a web browser, you should be able to view both the main channel here and the "Thread" that serves as The Stage in a split-screen presentation. This will let you have the channel and The Stage side by side.
